{"tid":1508743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾質疑元朗 721 警黑共管　區議員議辦被淋紅油","createTime":"2019-08-26T15:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T15:50:03.000Z","uid":68738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d39251691df78ed051d0b18497621d95a28bbf4c","tid":1508743,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/wong-08_d86ap_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwong-08_d86ap_1200x0.png&h=408b82c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗 721 白衣人襲擊市民事件後，該區民主黨區議員黃偉賢曾多次接受傳媒訪問，炮轟警方遲遲未到現場，質疑警方及黑社會「警黑共管」。他今日向《立場新聞》證實，近月被人滋擾、跟蹤及恐嚇，其辦事處今日亦被人淋紅油。他相信事件與其連日的言論有關。<br />\n<br />\n黃偉賢今日接受《立場新聞》訪問時表示，今早約8時有保安發現其辦事處被人淋紅油，推斷疑犯是在凌晨時間犯案。辦事處職員已報警並落口供。<br />\n<br />\n他坦言早有心理準備，因為自 6 月已不斷被人滋擾。在 721 元朗襲擊案中，有白衣人上前拍攝他的樣貌。之後數日亦有三名白衣人，先後在朗屏站外的天橋恐嚇：「你再搞嘢打你一鑊。」<br />\n<br />\n到 8 月 12 日他離開辦事處時，疑有人偷拍及跟蹤他。他當日已寫信給元朗指揮官講述事件，但未獲警方回應。16 日其辦事處收到恐嚇信，上面寫有「藉詞作亂 破壞治安 倒﹙搗﹚亂社會 小心門戶」的警告字眼，並潑有一些紅色液體。<br />\n<br />\n黃偉賢認為今次恐嚇事件是與其反送中言論有關，但無法推斷是黑社會抑或是政治對手所為，期望警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n元朗 721 襲擊事件後，黃偉賢曾高調接受傳媒訪問，稱在一日前已收到朋友消息指有人將會動員搞事。他稱有聯絡元朗區警民關係組，警方亦指他們「收到風」，將會安排部署。事發當日白衣人士圍毆市民前，他亦曾五度致電警方要求跟進，惟警方遲遲未到現場。<br />\n<br />\n他之後亦接受過電台訪問，稱721當晚有三名白衣人上前揚言打他，他向身邊一部警車上的警員要求保護時，警車竟即時駛走，他形容事件是「警黑共管」，怒斥警方「放水」讓黑社會打人然後為其善後，雙方似有「默契」行事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/WhatsApp20Image202019-08-2620at208.47.2420PM2028129_kz72i_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FWhatsApp20Image202019-08-2620at208.47.2420PM2028129_kz72i_1200x0.jpeg&h=12e1468d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/WhatsApp20Image202019-08-2620at208.47.2320PM_3sWpz_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FWhatsApp20Image202019-08-2620at208.47.2320PM_3sWpz_1200x0.jpeg&h=360ffa32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9B%BE%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-721-%E8%AD%A6%E9%BB%91%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%B0%E8%BE%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%B7%8B%E7%B4%85%E6%B2%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-721-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%25AE%25A1-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25B7%258B%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%25B2%25B9%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=17c964f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-721-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%25AE%25A1-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25B7%258B%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%25B2%25B9%2F&h=e0f607d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9B%BE%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-721-%E8%AD%A6%E9%BB%91%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%B0%E8%BE%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%B7%8B%E7%B4%85%E6%B2%B9/</a>"},{"pid":"821de38d648e38c788137744800200552028be97","tid":1508743,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=af68a8ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyo